OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,FA prominent Welsh Labour candidate has
OL,7,Finsisted First Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,8,Fstill has "fight in her", despite an
OL,9,FITV Cymru Wales poll showing she is on
OL,10,Fcourse to lose her seat in May's
OL,11,FSenedd election.
OL,13,FChris Carter told ITV's political
OL,14,Fprogramme Sharp End, "What you can see
OL,15,Ffrom the government is the fight that
OL,16,Fis inside the First Minister at the
OL,17,Fmoment."
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@XO]vD@VOUyD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
