CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1774455107
OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,F"We're fighting for every single vote
OL,7,Fin this campaign, whether it's in her
OL,8,Fconstituency or whether it's in my
OL,9,Fconstituency in Casnewydd Islwyn.
OL,11,F"We live in the age of the poly-
OL,12,Fcrisis, we've got war, we've got an
OL,13,Fenergy crisis, and we're still
OL,14,Frecovering from war, (and) the effects
OL,15,Fof Britain's exit from the European
OL,16,FUnion here in Wales."
OL,18,FThe poll forecasts Labour will not win
OL,19,Fany seats in several constituencies,
OL,20,Fincluding Baroness Morgan's.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@VpmvD@ZpnxD@UO]
