OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,FIt's the latest blow for Welsh Labour,
OL,7,Fwhich has landed in third place after
OL,8,Fhitting its lowest point in January's
OL,9,Fpoll.
OL,11,FDespite a drop in vote share to 33%,
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru is still on course to be
OL,13,Fthe largest party with a seat
OL,14,Fprojection suggesting it could win 43
OL,15,Fseats, leaving Rhun ap Iorwerth six
OL,16,Fshort of forming an overall majority
OL,17,Fin the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
