OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,FReacting to the poll, Reform's
OL,7,FFrancesca O'Brien described it as a
OL,8,Fpositive result. She said, "I think
OL,9,Fit's a positive result for us, we've
OL,10,Fgot a new leader here in Wales, Dan
OL,11,FThomas, and that poll is showing that
OL,12,Fwe are narrowing that gap."
OL,14,F"There is still appetite for Reform,
OL,15,Fyou could see there in Swansea, my
OL,16,Fhometown, that there is a need for
OL,17,Fchange. Reform is going to deliver
OL,18,Fthat change.
OL,26,@pD@\OUtD@[O]vD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
