PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1774455107
OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,F"Our message is quite clear, it's a
OL,7,Ftwo-horse race between Reform UK Wales
OL,8,Fand Plaid Cymru."
OL,10,FThe Deputy Green Party leader in
OL,11,FWales, Phil Davies, said: "It's really
OL,12,Fpositive, what it shows more than
OL,13,Fanything under this new system if you
OL,14,Fwant the party in power, if you want
OL,15,Fthe party elected, you can vote for
OL,16,Fthem across Wales, and you will get
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]sD@[OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
