PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1774455107
OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,F"The poll is quite similar to where it
OL,7,Fwas a few months ago for us, which is
OL,8,Fpositive as well. It shows we're
OL,9,Fstaying relevant in people's minds
OL,10,Fcoming into the election, and at the
OL,11,Fend of the day, we're the only party
OL,12,Fthat hasn't been in the Senedd before,
OL,13,Fso we're actually offering that
OL,14,Fpositive change that people want in
OL,15,Ftheir lives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
