PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1774455107
OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,F"What those numbers do do is inspire
OL,7,Fme to get out there, get the message
OL,8,Facross, and remind people that in
OL,9,FWales we've had a Labour government
OL,10,Fhere for 27 years, propped up time and
OL,11,Ftime again by the separatists in Plaid
OL,12,FCymru, and what have they delivered?
OL,13,FThey deliver the longest waitlist in
OL,14,Fthe UK, the worst economic outcomes in
OL,15,Fthe UK, and the worst education
OL,16,Foutcomes across the UK."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@XO]
