OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,FRodney Berman's party, the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats, are not expected to win any
OL,8,Fseats, according to the poll. He said,
OL,9,F"I think there are different ways of
OL,10,Finterpreting these figures. I've
OL,11,Flooked at different analyses of these
OL,12,Ffigures, and some of them show us
OL,13,Fgetting seats out of it."
OL,15,F"I don't think this poll picks up the
OL,16,Ffact that the Liberal Democrats aren't
OL,17,Fcampaigning uniformly across all
OL,18,Fconstituencies in Wales. We're
OL,19,Fcompeting very hard in pockets, where
OL,20,Fwe perhaps have more traditionally had
OL,21,Fsupport, like in mid-Wales.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@YO]wD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
