PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1774455107
OL,3,CFM still has 'fight in her', says
OL,4,CLabour candidate, despite poll result
OL,6,F"I think maybe that's not picked up in
OL,7,Fthese Wales-wide figures, and I think
OL,8,Fwe'll actually see a much better
OL,9,Fresult when we actually get to May 8th.
OL,11,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,12,Four political experts are across all
OL,13,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,14,Fto the latest episode below...
